<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>About Us - Html To Node</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
  <style>
    /* General Reset */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    /* Body Styling */
    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      color: #333;
    }

    /* Header Styling */
    header {
      background-color: #0da5c8;
      color: white;
      padding: 15px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .logo h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #fff;
      padding-top: 9px;
    }

    /* Main Content Styling */
    main {
      padding: 20px;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 42px;
      color: #4796c6;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      animation: fadeIn 1s ease;
    }

    h4 {
      font-size: 22px;
      color: #0f7f8a;
      margin: 15px 0;
      padding: 10px;
      background-color: #e9f1ff;
      border-left: 5px solid #27b7a3;
      border-radius: 5px;
      animation: fadeIn 1s ease;
    }

    /* Paragraph Styling */
    p {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 16px;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
      animation: slideIn 1s ease;
    }

    p:hover {
      transform: scale(1.02);
    }

    /* Team Member Styling */
    .team-container {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .team-member {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      padding: 15px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 10px;
      flex: 1 1 calc(33% - 20px);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .team-member img {
      border-radius: 50%;
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
    }

    .team-member h5 {
      margin: 10px 0;
    }

    .team-member a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 10px;
      padding: 5px 10px;
      background-color: #0da5c8;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 5px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }

    .team-member a:hover {
      background-color: #007bff;
    }

    /* Footer Styling */
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 40px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #777;
    }

    /* Keyframe animations */
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
      }

      to {
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }

    @keyframes slideIn {
      from {
        transform: translateY(20px);
        opacity: 0;
      }

      to {
        transform: translateY(0);
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }

    /* Responsive adjustments */
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      h1 {
        font-size: 32px;
      }

      h4 {
        font-size: 18px;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      .team-member {
        flex: 1 1 calc(100% - 20px);
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <!-- Navigation -->
  <header>
    <div class="logo">
      <h1>MyWebsite</h1>
    </div>
    <nav class="navbar">
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
        <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
        <li><a href="/products">Products</a></li>
      </ul>
      <div class="hamburger">
        <span class="bar"></span>
        <span class="bar"></span>
        <span class="bar"></span>
      </div>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <main>
    <h1>About Us</h1>
    <p>Welcome to MyWebsite, where we are committed to delivering a seamless user experience through dynamic content and
      personalized services. Our platform offers a variety of features, including a detailed Product Catalog linked
      directly to our database, allowing you to explore our diverse range of products effortlessly.</p>

    <h4>1. Company/Project Background</h4>
    <p>Details about the company or the purpose of the project. Here, you can share the vision and mission that drives
      your organization.</p>

    <h4>2. Product or Service Descriptions</h4>
    <p>Information on the products or services offered. Highlight key offerings that set you apart from the competition.
    </p>

    <h4>3. Team Members</h4>
    <div class="team-container">
      <div class="team-member">
        <img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLLoKl9QjODxgUjoy6bI5JmnbwbYHO4PU2te74MXo3WYjkuFgM=s83-c-mo"
          alt="Team Member 1">
        <h5>Sujit Singh</h5>
        <p>CEO & Founder</p>
        <a href="#">View Profile</a>
      </div>
      <div class="team-member">
        <img
          src="https://static.vecteezy.com/system/resources/thumbnails/036/338/921/small/ai-generated-friendly-businessman-offering-handshake-in-office-photo.jpg"
          alt="Team Member 2">
        <h5>Jane Smith</h5>
        <p>Lead Developer</p>
        <a href="#">View Profile</a>
      </div>
      <div class="team-member">
        <img src="https://cdn.openart.ai/published/QPGIgm7NocL80xl3z35R/CQHqnJKN_Yr8u_1024.webp" alt="Team Member 3">
        <h5>Emily Johnson</h5>
        <p>Marketing Manager</p>
        <a href="#">View Profile</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h4>4. Technology Stack</h4>
    <p>Technical details about the tools and frameworks used in development. Mention the technologies that power your
      platform.</p>

    <h4>5. User Guidance</h4>
    <p>Instructions on how to navigate or use the website's features. Provide tips for users to get the most out of your
      site.</p>
  </main>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer>
    &copy; 2024 MyWebsite. All rights reserved.
  </footer>

  <script>
    // Hamburger menu toggle for mobile view
    const hamburger = document.querySelector('.hamburger');
    const navLinks = document.querySelector('.nav-links');

    hamburger.addEventListener('click', () => {
      navLinks.classList.toggle('nav-active');
      hamburger.classList.toggle('toggle');
    });
  </script>
</body>

</html>